Package de.oth.blocklib.server

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ServerContext
    The context of the server and the server specific singletons
    ServerEntityManager
    The EntityManager for the server to handle the entities and message the clients about it
    The WorldGenerator must be build before the ServerEntityManager is build
    ServerListenerManager
    Contains all listeners for the network messages that can be send to a server
    For additional listeners use the pattern:
    networkManager.registerMessageListener(YourNewNetworkClass.class, (NetworkMessage networkMessage, NetworkConnection networkConnection) -> { your code to be executed});
    Dont forget to add your new message class to the MessageRegistry
    ServerNpcCreator
    Stores blueprints and creates npcs
    ServerWorldInteraction
    The WorldInteraction for the server to interact with the world and message the clients about it
